Title: Go to the Priory
Description:
I... I do not have the words. Theleon...

I will take h-his body. They will know what to do at the priory.

Oh, brother... It was not supposed to end like this...
ObjectivesText: Meet Sister Etna Blayze at the Priory of the Sacred Flame.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet with Sister Etna Blayze at the Priory of the Sacred Flame.
RewardText: So young to have been taken from us. So brave and bold. Perhaps too bold.
